Q: 停场在Manassas Regl Davis的所有航司有哪些？
SQL:
SELECT
    DISTINCT supplier_name
FROM
    zts_plane_status
WHERE
    status = 0
    AND supplier_name IS NOT NULL
    AND pure_reg IN (
        SELECT
            LOWER(REPLACE(REPLACE(registration, ' ', ''), '-', ''))
        FROM
            dc_aircraft
        WHERE
            delete_tag = 0
    )
    AND arr_icao = "KHEF" COLLATE utf8mb4_general_ci;
actual_SQL:
SELECT
    DISTINCT supplier_name
FROM
    zts_plane_status
WHERE
    status = 0
    AND supplier_name IS NOT NULL
    AND pure_reg IN (
        SELECT
            LOWER(REPLACE(REPLACE(registration, ' ', ''), '-', ''))
        FROM
            dc_aircraft

            delete_tag = 0
    )
